  "Presto!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_textAboveHeadEvent6",
  "Ah... You're right on time, @!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event7",
  "Let me just set the table...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event7_sv1",
  "You've been working so hard on the farm... I wanted to make you a special dinner.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event8",
  "It's my very own 'angel hair pasta primavera'... with clams!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event9",
  "Heavenly, huh? That must be the 'angel hair'!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event10",
  "I'm glad you like it! You deserve the best.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event10_sv1",
  "Oh yes, I forgot to mention... it's 'whole wheat' pasta. And it's brimming with fresh vegetables.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event11",
  "It's important that you eat healthy food! I want you to live forever...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event11_sv1",
  "Oh... I see. I knew I needed to add more salt.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event12",
  "Well, at least you'll be well hydrated.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event12_sv1",
  "Oh... I thought I gave myself the burnt one.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event13",
  "Um, I lost track of one the pans and it caught fire... Sorry, dear.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event13_sv1",
  "Uhhh...! Heh. I guess a piece of my moustache may have fallen into the pasta...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event14",
  "Well! Extra fiber, right? Heh... (sorry honey)": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event14_sv1",
  "Oh! Eh... Must've been the truffle oil I drizzled on top...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event15",
  "You meant delicious, edible fungus... right honey? Of course... Heh.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event15_sv1",
  "So, tell me about your day...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event16",
  "Yes, I can still see the dirt in your hair! I really appreciate all the hard work you do, honey.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event17",
  "That sounds dangerous... are you sure that's safe?": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event18",
  "I don't want to see you on the operating table anytime soon...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event18_sv1",
  "Although I have to say, I like how courageous you are...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event18_sv2",
  "A peaceful day by the water, huh? That sounds very relaxing.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event19",
  "I'm glad you're having fun out there!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event19_sv1",
  "Ah, that's good. Having an active social life is healthy for the brain.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event20",
  "But remember, I'm always here for you if you need someone to talk to!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event20_sv1",
  "That makes sense. There's lots to do in this valley! ...And I know how hard you work.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event21",
  "Just remember to take breaks! When you're so busy, it's easy to get burnt out from exhaustion.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event21_sv1",
  "Ah... I have that problem, too. The boundary between days can blur together... it's hard to keep track of everything!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event22",
  "Took the day off, huh? I'm glad to hear it.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event23",
  "Well, with a day off and a hearty dinner you'll be fully re-charged for tomorrow.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event23_sv1",
  "Whew... I'm stuffed! That was great...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event24",
  "I'll take care of the dishes...": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event25",
  "Don't feel bad... I like to do nice things for you! It makes me happy.": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event26",
  "I know I say this a lot, but... marrying you was the best thing that ever happened to me!": "FarmHouse_3917626_Harvey_L_Harvey_event27",
